  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Vino</title>

    <para>The <application>Vino</application> package is a VNC server for
    <application>GNOME</application>. VNC is a protocol that allows remote
    display of a user's desktop.</para>

    &lfs65_checked;

